column5: I havew reservations for next year (2005) for a week at a camp on Lac Suel. I need some one interested in going along and splitting expenses. I have 19ft boat motorand trailer and truck. Only need some one with fishing pole and tackle. The cabin has no bathroom, But has hot and cold water. It is for the first part of june for 1 week. Leaving from Mankato, Minnesota. Please e-mail me for more details. Cost is about $450-500 american including gas, meals, lodging and etc. Thanks
What camp are you staying at and what is your e-mail address?
